summary: This module manages WebDAV live property namespaces and property lookups for the Apache HTTP Server's mod_dav module. It provides functions to register, retrieve, and enumerate WebDAV property namespaces and to map between property IDs and specifications.

logs.reason: Outputs XML namespace declarations for WebDAV live properties to be included in XML responses. This is not an error message but part of normal WebDAV XML response formatting.
logs.resolution: Information output, no resolution required. If this appears malformed in responses, check for proper namespace URI registration and pool memory management.
